rComments: Meilleure prof de didactique que j'ai eu à date en trois ans d'université. Madame Hamel est réellement passionnée par les technologies éducatives et est toujours prête à en discuter. Elle est vraiment formidable. Il n'y a pas d'examens dans son cours.

I took this course out of my normal faculty to continue improving my French and help improve my GPA. She was so kind and caring and really a great lecturer as well. There were many projects but they were unique and doable as well. I highly recommend taking her courses as she clearly cares for her students,
